</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE519783E473C6C9EACFBF1F692FB95" blockId="13.[174,1233,807,1463]" box="[174,1232,1124,1146]" pageId="13" pageNumber="208">
<keyLead id="30ABBA4D3E473C6C9EACFBF1F692FB95" box="[174,1232,1124,1146]" pageId="13" pageNumber="208">4b. Proboscis with 26–34 longitudinal hook rows of 19–21 hooks....................................................................5</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="30AE01DD3E473C6C9EACFB14F692FB3F" pageId="13" pageNumber="208">
<paragraph id="8BE519783E473C6C9EACFB14F692FB78" blockId="13.[174,1233,807,1463]" box="[174,1232,1153,1175]" pageId="13" pageNumber="208">
<keyLead id="30ABBA4D3E473C6C9EACFB14F692FB78" box="[174,1232,1153,1175]" pageId="13" pageNumber="208">
5а. Proboscis with 26–30 longitudinal hook rows. Blade of the largest hook 42 length. ........... 
